com.zhuinden.simplestack.navigator

Interface DefaultStateChanger.ViewChangeStartListener

  • Enclosing class:
    DefaultStateChanger

    public static interface DefaultStateChanger.ViewChangeStartListener
    Allows the possibility of listening to when the view change is to start, after the views are inflated and state is restored, but before view change is started.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  DefaultStateChanger.ViewChangeStartListener.Callback
      Notifies the DefaultStateChanger that the view change start listener completed its callback.
